Ep 4: Zoe Much To Do, Zoe Little Time

PREMIERE: Wednesday March 27, 9:00 pm
 
Rachel returns from Paris exhausted and faces an overbooked schedule, including an InStyle Magazine shoot with actress Jaime King and a hosting gig for a celebrity polo match. But when she encounters issues with her collection that would be better handled in New York, she reaches a breaking point and contemplates getting an apartment in New York.
